.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, almond-milk, mirinda, milk, cola, hot-chocolate
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, american, polish, argentine, pakistani, canadian, indian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, badminton, rowing, rugby, lacrosse, biathlon, ice-hockey
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, boat, car, tram, skateboard, airplane, trike
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the argentine##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the american is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the turkish is on the right of the indian##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 7. the person driving the trike is on the right of the pakistani##1
 8. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the trike and the canadian##2
 9. the pakistani is on the right of the person driving the car##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking milk##1
12. the person drinking milk is the person driving the scooter##1
13. the person drinking water is on the left of the polish##1
14. the canadian is the person driving the car##1
15. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the indian##1
16. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
17. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the polish##1
18. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the pakistani##1
19. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | cola        | milk | almond-milk      | mirinda     | water      | hot-chocolate     |
